---
import RootLayout from "../layouts/RootLayout.astro";
---

<RootLayout title="Terms of Service — Kowyo Cloud" description="Terms of Service for Kowyo Cloud">
	<main class="max-w-2xl mx-auto px-6 py-16 text-zinc-300">
		<h1 class="text-3xl font-semibold text-zinc-50 mb-2">Terms of Service</h1>
		<p class="text-zinc-500 text-sm mb-10">Last updated: March 18, 2026</p>

		<section class="mb-8">
			<h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-zinc-100 mb-3">1. About Kowyo Cloud</h2>
			<p class="leading-7">Kowyo Cloud ("we," "us," or "our") provides next-generation cloud compute infrastructure for AI-intensive applications. By using our services, you agree to these Terms of Service.</p>
		</section>

		<section class="mb-8">
			<h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-zinc-100 mb-3">2. Eligibility</h2>
			<p class="leading-7">You must be at least 18 years old and capable of entering into a legally binding agreement to use our services. By using Kowyo Cloud, you represent that you meet these requirements.</p>
		</section>

		<section class="mb-8">
			<h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-zinc-100 mb-3">3. Acceptable Use</h2>
			<p class="leading-7">You agree not to use our services for any unlawful purpose, to transmit malicious code, to interfere with or disrupt our infrastructure, or to violate any applicable laws or regulations, including export control laws.</p>
		</section>

		<section class="mb-8">
			<h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-zinc-100 mb-3">4. Subscription and Billing</h2>
			<p class="leading-7">Kowyo Cloud offers subscription-based plans billed on a recurring basis. By subscribing, you authorize us to charge your payment method on the applicable billing cycle. All fees are exclusive of taxes, which you are responsible for.</p>
		</section>

		<section class="mb-8">
			<h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-zinc-100 mb-3">5. Cancellation Policy</h2>
			<p class="leading-7">You may cancel your subscription at any time from your account dashboard or by contacting us at <a href="mailto:hi@kowyo.com" class="text-zinc-100 underline">hi@kowyo.com</a>. Cancellation takes effect at the end of the current billing period. You will retain access to the service until the period ends.</p>
		</section>

		<section class="mb-8">
			<h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-zinc-100 mb-3">6. Refund and Dispute Policy</h2>
			<p class="leading-7 mb-3">We offer a 7-day money-back guarantee for new subscribers on first-time purchases. If you are unsatisfied within 7 days of your initial payment, contact us at <a href="mailto:hi@kowyo.com" class="text-zinc-100 underline">hi@kowyo.com</a> and we will issue a full refund.</p>
			<p class="leading-7 mb-3">After the 7-day period, subscription fees are non-refundable except where required by applicable law.</p>
			<p class="leading-7">If you believe you have been charged in error, contact us at <a href="mailto:hi@kowyo.com" class="text-zinc-100 underline">hi@kowyo.com</a> within 30 days of the charge. We will investigate and respond within 5 business days. If we are unable to resolve your dispute, you may contact your card issuer or payment provider to initiate a chargeback.</p>
		</section>

		<section class="mb-8">
			<h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-zinc-100 mb-3">7. Service Availability</h2>
			<p class="leading-7">We strive for high availability but do not guarantee uninterrupted service. We are not liable for any downtime, data loss, or damages resulting from service interruptions.</p>
		</section>

		<section class="mb-8">
			<h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-zinc-100 mb-3">8. Legal and Export Restrictions</h2>
			<p class="leading-7">Our services are subject to the export control laws and regulations of the United States and other applicable jurisdictions. You agree not to use our services in violation of these laws, including using them in any country embargoed by the U.S. government or on behalf of any individual or entity prohibited by applicable export control laws.</p>
		</section>

		<section class="mb-8">
			<h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-zinc-100 mb-3">9. Promotions</h2>
			<p class="leading-7">Any promotional offers or discounts are subject to specific terms communicated at the time of the promotion. Promotions cannot be combined unless explicitly stated and may be withdrawn at any time without prior notice.</p>
		</section>

		<section class="mb-8">
			<h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-zinc-100 mb-3">10. Changes to These Terms</h2>
			<p class="leading-7">We may update these terms from time to time. We will notify you of material changes via email or a prominent notice on our website. Continued use of the service after changes constitutes acceptance of the updated terms.</p>
		</section>

		<section class="mb-8">
			<h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-zinc-100 mb-3">11. Contact</h2>
			<p class="leading-7">For questions about these Terms, contact us at <a href="mailto:hi@kowyo.com" class="text-zinc-100 underline">hi@kowyo.com</a>.</p>
		</section>

		<div class="mt-12 pt-6 border-t border-zinc-800 flex gap-6 text-sm text-zinc-500">
			<a href="/" class="hover:text-zinc-300">Home</a>
			<a href="/privacy" class="hover:text-zinc-300">Privacy Policy</a>
		</div>
	</main>
</RootLayout>
